			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-787005">
									

<p>Author-</p>
<p>How much does Fred adapt to the book? Like, if the main characters of the book are vampires, does he become a vampire? Or even non-humans, as in if he's in a book where the main characters are wolves?</p>
<p>More to the point, can he sustain damage/death in a book, and still make it back out? There's a couple tests I'd like to add, but I'd like to know the authors thoughts first.</p>
<p>Also, deleted the Deadpool test. Too much 'for the lulz,' 'Fan wank' and just out of line.</p>

