			<div class="content" id="post-content-792042">
									

<p>I would like to protest vehemently, the Deadpool test was just fine. I might just have replaced the fan-wank notes at the end with something a bit more skeptical and/or shocked and detached, but the test itself did fit, and make sense in context as well.</p>
<p>As for your other questions, weren't those pretty well answered in the main article?</p>

