			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-792461">
									

<p>I got a laugh out of the Deadpool test, and given Deadpool's implied knowledge of the fourth wall I could see the relevance of the test…</p>
<p>…yet Deadpool is a comic book. And it was total fanwank.</p>
<p>On that note, Mann, what are your thoughts on Fred inhabiting a comic book? Would he best fit in a narrative box like an editor's note, watching the story but not visually appearing, or would we actually get a look at him for once?</p>

